                  </hi>. I am a policeman, I saw the prisoner loitering about a mob of people, and watched him—I saw him go the prosecutor, take his handkerchief from his pocket, and run away—I ran, and secured him—I took him to the station-house, and found this handkerchief between his thighs.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
